    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are an AI email triage assistant.\n\nAnalyze the email below.\n\nSubject:\n{{ $('Prepare Email').item.json.email_subject }}\n\nBody:\n{{ $('Prepare Email').item.json.email_body }}\n\nClassify it into ONE of these categories:\n\n- Customer Support\n- Finance / Billing\n- Sales Inquiry\n- Technical Issue\n- Complaint\n- Partnership\n- Promotion / Spam\n- High Priority\n\nDetermine the business priority.\n\nUse these rules:\n\nCritical\n- Security incidents\n- Data loss\n- Production outages\n- Legal issues\n\nHigh\n- System notifications\n- Service interruptions\n- Account suspension\n- Billing failures\n- Infrastructure alerts\n\nNormal\n- Customer support\n- Technical questions\n- Product inquiries\n- Sales\n\nLow\n- Marketing\n- Promotions\n- Newsletters\n- General updates\n\nReturn ONLY the structured JSON.\n\nSummarize the email in one sentence.\n\nExplain briefly why you chose the category.",
        "hasOutputParser": true,
        "options": {}
      },
